text: Novosharipovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Sokolovsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 59 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 10 km from Davlekanovo, 2 km from Sokolovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Novosharipovo
